This version of DiskSim 4.0 has been modified in order
to be used with HP Labs COTSon. 

The current directory has two patch files that 
corresponds to the changes made in DiskSim to adapt it 
to COTSon:

- patch-64bits: Changes needed to compile and use DiskSim
	version 4.0 in a 64-bit machine.

- patch-cotson: Changes needed to create a library that can 
	be linked into COTSon.
	

To apply the patches, download DiskSim 4.0 from 
http://www.pdl.cmu.edu/DiskSim/, and execute:

$ cd disksim-4.0
$ patch -p1 < patch-64bits
$ patch -p1 < patch-cotson

